Package: missOutlier
Title: Outlier Detection Using the MISS Method
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Guillaume", "Pech", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "guillaumepech.cog@gmail.com")
Description: Detects outliers using the MISS method, a weighted combination of
    Median Absolute Deviation (MAD), Interquartile Range (IQR), and Standard
    Deviation (SD) thresholds.
